        <content>
          <p>CHAPTER 6.  ACCEPTANCE AND RENUNCIATION
OF SUCCESSIONS
SECTION 1.
GENERAL PRINCIPLES
Art. 947.  Right of successor to accept or renounce
A successor is not obligated to accept rights to succeed.  He may accept some of those rights and renounce others.</p>
        </content>
